{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"b650f840-16f9-4d2d-bc45-266b3372e64a","content":"**MSTest.Sdk 4.x dropped the VSTest adapter by default.** Starting with v4.0, the SDK exclusively targets **Microsoft.Testing.Platform** and no longer ships the VSTest bridge that `vstest.console.exe` relies on to discover and run tests.\n\n### How to fix\n\n**Option A – Switch your CI to `dotnet test` (recommended):**\n\n```bash\ndotnet test TestProject.csproj\n```\n\n`dotnet test` works natively with Microsoft.Testing.Platform in SDK 4.x.\n\n**Option B – Re-enable the VSTest bridge** if you must keep `vstest.console`:\n\nAdd this to your `.csproj`:\n\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>true</EnableMicrosoftTestingPlatformVSTestBridge>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\nThis pulls in the compatibility layer so `vstest.console` can discover tests again.\n\n### Why it changed\n\nMicrosoft.Testing.Platform is the modern replacement for VSTest, offering faster startup and native `dotnet test` integration. MSTest.Sdk 4.x made it the sole default to simplify the dependency graph.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"522ac2ff-f5fa-4743-9f86-cf84e647daf6","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about a known breaking change in MSTest.Sdk. Starting with MSTest.Sdk 3.x, the SDK used Microsoft.Testing.Platform by default but still supported VSTest. In MSTest.Sdk 4.0+, VSTest support was removed by default.\n\nThe key change: **MSTest.Sdk 4.0+ no longer includes the VSTest runner/adapter by default.** The SDK now exclusively targets Microsoft.Testing.Platform. If your CI uses `vstest.console.exe` to run tests, it won't discover tests because the VSTest adapter (`Microsoft.VisualStudio.TestPlatform.MSTest.TestAdapter`) is no longer included.\n\n\nTo fix this, I can either switch the CI to use `dotnet test` which natively supports Microsoft.Testing.Platform, re-enable VSTest compatibility by adding a project property, or configure dotnet test support directly in the project file.","outputTokens":674,"requestId":"1BCD:AAEEE:BE3D90:D7348F:6A03F2AB"},"id":"9f138b4c-af48-4c65-981f-5b2991c4a07c","timestamp":"2026-05-13T03:40:42.505Z","parentId":"1e6d50ad-1806-4bdc-979a-ab5e56c22ced"}
